<note n="0223001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0223001">此為 triṣṭubh 調之一偈所插入者，底本附以三、四兩節之號碼為錯誤，四節之號碼應除去。</note>
<note n="0225001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0225001">Rohiṇi（赤牛）。</note>
<note n="0226001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226001">Sunanda（善喜）。</note>
<note n="0226002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226002">讀為 ayājiyiṁ（異本）。以下同樣原文用第三人稱之動詞應訂正為一人稱。此處婆羅門係指長者之前生。</note>
<note n="0226003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0226003">讀為 aphari satte（暹羅本）。參閱前之第六八菴婆達耶迦長老之第一偈。</note>
<note n="0227001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0227001">Vasabha（牡牛）。</note>
<note n="0227002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0227002">以下同應視為第一人稱。</note>
<note n="0228003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0228003">Siridhara（吉祥持）。</note>
<note n="0229001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0229001">Vihatābha（殺光）。</note>
<note n="0229001-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0229001-1">讀為 puragacchi so（暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0230002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0230002">Sukhitta（善投）。</note>
<note n="0230001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0230001">Kesava（美髮）。</note>
<note n="0230002-1" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0230002-1">Amittavāsana（無敵住）。</note>
<note n="0231003" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0231003">讀為 Ekaraṁsaniya（暹羅本及他異本）。</note>
<note n="0231001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0231001">讀為 Sasākhaṁ。</note>
<note n="0231002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0231002">Virocana（徧照）。</note>
<note n="0232001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0232001">讀為 Parapāṇu。</note>
<note n="0233001" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0233001">讀為 Ekaraṁsi（異本及暹羅本）。</note>
<note n="0233002" resp="#resp1" place="foot text" type="orig" target="#nkr_note_orig_0233002">Sāladada = Sālapupphadāyaka。</note>
</p>
